{"tid":1446600,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【文宣請入】警狗冒充示威者 係分化藍絲陣營嘅好機會","createTime":"2019-08-11T15:08:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:48:29.000Z","uid":302390,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"0031177b71c2cd75466319dc7c36254c48692a1f","tid":1446600,"uid":302390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:08:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\">【文宣請入】警狗冒充示威者 係分化藍絲陣營嘅好機會</span><br />\n<br />\n冇錯，黑警冒充前線抗爭者，甚至煽動前線去送死，喺我哋內部需要好好宣傳、避免前線中伏。<br />\n<br />\n但係，對於一啲想繁榮安定、覺得警察係維持治安嘅藍絲，佢哋喺得悉呢一件事之後，<strong>只會覺得「警察好醒」、「諗到出卧底呢一招」</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n所以，要分化深藍陣營，就要塑造<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">陰謀論</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">（藍絲廢老唔會同證據，只有聽落言之有理就得，所以先會成日share啲假消息），</span>將<span style=\"color: red;\">「警察」同「平民安危」兩樣野造成對立</span>；我有以下兩個方向，希望拋磚引玉：<br />\n<br />\n1. 講話<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>大陸/香港政府內部/警察內部嘅權鬥</strong></span></span>利用香港嘅示威，製造混亂，希望拉部分官員引咎下台，從而上位。所以利用部分警員煽動示威者、甚至帶頭搞事，搞到成件事愈來愈亂，令港人人心惶惶，即使普通嘅市民都大受影響。大陸/港政/警察內部已經係分做兩派人、甚至幾派人嘅內鬥（大陸可以係江派對習派，警察可以係一哥對二哥），佢哋係唔會理市民大眾嘅利益，只係想奪權、奪權同埋奪權。<br />\n<br />\n2. 就係<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">警察內部想擴大自己實權</span></strong>，原理同上，所以一致營造示威者暴力嘅行徑，令追求法治、和平普通市民對佢哋更加依賴、開始默許佢哋嘅濫權，令佢哋權力過大，一發不可收拾，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">連張建宗司長都夠膽反，完全違反公務員要對長官忠誠嘅條文。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n最後，喺文宣上加多啲「已證實」、「重大消息」等嘅字眼都可以增加藍絲嘅信服。<br />\n<br />\n附上文宣圖片兩張<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RaT205e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRaT205e.jpg&h=9b9b82e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DMGgk5n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDMGgk5n.jpg&h=42de28b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外請看：<br />\n[請推]LAW- 卧底引導犯罪，叫Entrapment<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1445683\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1445683</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f6152a2e7a38bf4feaac8f8e163a66c6b7f506f5","tid":1446600,"uid":302390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:08:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eb44a8957c9070e0f95220329ac6e3a8c592326a","tid":1446600,"uid":302390,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:08:53.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"e2c7de1f67f8e1465be7189ff75129180b013e37","tid":1446600,"uid":302390,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:09:11.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"47eb0e52c7128a0b90e7684657db31294af541ae","tid":1446600,"uid":302390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:09:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"223f7a38c1dc11e6fac3a379b7ebd3b762f72361","tid":1446600,"uid":302390,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:09:34.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"f584453dda0b9489436aa4003e05b12ea72429e4","tid":1446600,"uid":302390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:10:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cf7ab79e0854d202ba7e2154889ddb9c2e4a460c","tid":1446600,"uid":302390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:11:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7ef436626ea22349282c7429f574cae2c15836ca","tid":1446600,"uid":277702,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:11:17.000Z","msg":"根本所有暴力衝擊都係呢班人做囉"},{"pid":"59a699b775676c98a935bb93ca2e82efa1fd5556","tid":1446600,"uid":302390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:11:19.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"c87419aca341a1e80044daed7e7997f4e04927ae","tid":1446600,"uid":302390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:11:33.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"6fcbb1c67b61d8c3e0b3314c94be6ead54924713","tid":1446600,"uid":269694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:11:54.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"84557961269cbdd46fefc23a3004ea356dd14d78","tid":1446600,"uid":12149,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTi