e.google.com/drive/u/0/folders/1699DS2mdmfWd1-wfBVoAiVpu6SP2rqpt\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fdrive%2Fu%2F0%2Ffolders%2F1699DS2mdmfWd1-wfBVoAiVpu6SP2rqpt&d=rP1lJsqA2sO3Td0%2BA1LJ5z%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=3191b084\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/drive/u/0/folders/1699DS2mdmfWd1-wfBVoAiVpu6SP2rqpt</a>"},{"pid":"fd980c645887a3b1bf0c49bff0ee1a4d8156fe26","tid":1446600,"uid":106937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:28:08.000Z","msg":"pushhhhhhhh"},{"pid":"5ee110da4e93128d0fe8255da486cfdfe64e4bee","tid":1446600,"uid":260639,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:29:54.000Z","msg":"in 陰毛論 we trust <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好講推 將今日核彈列明黎推post<br />\n1. 射頭爆眼<br />\n2. 721無起訴<br />\n3. 狗扮示威者<br />\n4. 室內射tear gas<br />\n5. 武警混入黑警，中共撕毀基本法<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n勇武要點我唔知<br />\n但和理非一定要升級！！<br />\n做得幾多得幾多<br />\n多你一個多好多<br />\n趁病打暴政<br />\n打蛇打七寸<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1444667/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1444667/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"e55116eb3882ea52dda512969726f550f3baadb0","tid":1446600,"uid":260639,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:33:44.000Z","msg":"長輩圖出動啦！！！"}]}